caller_intent: Alan needed assistance finalizing a payment for an insurance policy, resolving confusion between carriers (Chub vs. USLI), and confirming document receipt for an event-related insurance policy.
resolution_steps: Corbin clarified the correct carrier (USLI) after Alan mistakenly selected Chub.
Confirmed payment details, including credit card information, email, and cardholder name.
Processed the payment and verified its completion.
Checked whether Alan had received and signed the required document via email.
Provided confirmation that the payment was processed and the document was received.
knowledge_required: Carrier-specific insurance policies (e.g., USLI for events)
summary: Corbin assisted Alan in resolving a carrier mix-up, processed a payment for an event insurance policy, and confirmed document receipt. The call concluded with payment confirmation and a follow-up on the signed document. Alan expressed gratitude, and both parties agreed to stay in touch for future needs.
